summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 80E, page 188 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 8457 Rainier Avenue South from Single Family 5000 (SF500) to Lowrise 3 (L3) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Harvey Ho, C.F. 302825, Appl. 9703170).
